title: Zayo to Host First Quarter Fiscal Year 2016 Conference Call November 10, 2015
text:
Companies mentioned in this article: Zayo Group Holdings, Inc. 
BOULDER, Colo. -- (BUSINESS WIRE) -- Zayo Group Holdings (“Zayo” or the “Company”) (NYSE: ZAYO) invites you to listen to its earnings call for the first quarter fiscal year 2016 ended September 30, 2015 on Tuesday, November 10, 2015. 
When: Tuesday, November 10, 2015 @ 8:00 a.m. MT/10:00 a.m. ETClick this link to register and view the Webcast: https://cc.readytalk.com/r/x6lw7vtng5ks&eom Dial-in information for the audio portion of the Webcast: U.S. & Canada Toll-Free: 800-757-8473 
During the call, the Company will review an earnings presentation that summarizes the financial, operational and commercial highlights of the quarter. The earnings supplement, playback recording and earnings presentation will be available after the call through Zayo’s website at: http://www.zayo.com/investors/earnings-releases . 
If you have any questions, please contact Zayo Investor Relations at 303.381.3284 or IR@zayo.com . 
About Zayo Group 
Zayo Group Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: ZAYO) provides bandwidth infrastructure services, including fiber and bandwidth connectivity, colocation and cloud services to the world’s leading businesses. Customers include wireless and wireline carriers, media and content companies and finance, healthcare and other large enterprises. Zayo’s 85,500-mile network in the U.S. and Europe includes extensive metro connectivity to thousands of buildings and data centers. In addition to high-capacity dark fiber, wavelength, Ethernet and other connectivity solutions, Zayo offers colocation and cloud services in its carrier-neutral data centers. Zayo provides clients with flexible, customized solutions and self-service through Tranzact, an innovative online platform for managing and purchasing bandwidth and services.
